citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
Section 2.126(b)
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 11:10 - 11:40
am on 09/04/2014. Inspector knocked on residence door, honked vehicle horn, called listed phone number with no
response.
